  "title": "General Practitioner (GP) / Family Doctor | Up to $17K at Holland Village #HMA",
  "description": "<h2>🩺 <strong>Hiring: General Practitioner (GP) </strong><br />📍 Location: Holland Village<br />💰 Salary: Up to $17,000/month<br />📄 Employment Type: Permanent</h2><h3>👨‍⚕️ <strong>Job Scope</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Provide comprehensive primary care consultations</p></li><li><p>Diagnose and manage acute and chronic conditions</p></li><li><p>Prescribe medications and treatment plans appropriately</p></li><li><p>Conduct health screenings, vaccinations, and follow-ups</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate clinical documentation</p></li><li><p>Deliver patient-centred, ethical, and quality medical care</p></li></ul><h3>✅ <strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>MBBS or equivalent qualification</p></li><li><p>Fully registered with <strong>Singapore Medical Council (SMC)</strong></p></li><li><p>Valid Practising Certificate</p></li><li><p>GP / Primary care experience preferred</p></li><li><p>Good bedside manner and communication skills</p></li></ul><h3>✨ <strong>Why Join</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prime clinic location at <strong>Holland Village</strong></p></li><li><p>Attractive remuneration package (<strong>up to $17K</strong>)</p></li><li><p>Supportive clinic operations and nursing support</p></li><li><p>Stable patient load with reputable medical group<br /></p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Apply Now:</strong><br />📱 <strong>Tele / WhatsApp:</strong> +65 8598 2694<br />Or<br />📧 <strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Michelle@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p><strong>Michelle Ang – Recruit Express Pte Ltd</strong><br />Personnel CEI License No: <strong>R26159565</strong><br />Company License (EA): <strong>99C4599</strong></p>",
